    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "The NanoSwitch is an outdoor, 4-port Gigabit switch with PoE pass-through. It is powered by 24V Passive PoE and provides up to 24W of power on three PoE out ports. The NanoSwitch is designed for outdoor deployment and supports up to 4 Gbps total, non-blocking line rate."
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "Features"
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "- (1) Gigabit 24V Passive PoE In Port\n- (3) Gigabit 24V Passive PoE Out Ports\n- Outdoor, Weather-Resistant Enclosure"
    },
    {
      "heading": "Designed for Outdoor Durability",
      "text": "Designed for Outdoor Durability"
    },
    {
      "heading": "The NanoSwitch features an outdoor weatherproof form factor.\nOperating Temperature: -30 to 70° C (-22 to 158° F)",
      "text": "The NanoSwitch features an outdoor weatherproof form factor.\nOperating Temperature: -30 to 70° C (-22 to 158° F)",
