    {
      "heading": "Power Strip Simplicity for 24V Devices",
      "text": "Power Strip Simplicity for 24V Devices"
    },
    {
      "heading": "Simply providing 24V 2-pair input makes NanoSwitch an outdoor 4-port unmanaged switch with \"always on\" 24V 2-pair output on three ports.",
      "text": "Simply providing 24V 2-pair input makes NanoSwitch an outdoor 4-port unmanaged switch with \"always on\" 24V 2-pair output on three ports."
    },
    {
      "heading": "PoE Passthrough",
      "text": "PoE Passthrough"
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "PoE In — RJ45 port supports 10/100/1000 Ethernet connections, and supports passive 24V, 2-pair PoE to power the switch."
    },
    {
      "heading": "",
      "text": "PoE Out — RJ45 ports support 10/100/1000 Ethernet connections, and the three passive 24V, 2-pair PoE ports provide up to 30W PoE output."
